query:
select ts, mgmt_addr, meta_uuid, meta_event_name, 
                            meta_mgmturl, events_enrichment_target_process_node_key_value, 
                            events_enrichment_target_file_hashes_sha1, meta_agent_name, events_timestamp_millisecondssinceepoch
                            from hive_datalake.views.dv_events_table_mgmts
                            where events_enrichment_target_file_hashes_sha1 in ('9af1b128133af4f9e0f812fe71849785cc47aed9') and
                            ts >= '2021-10-14' and 
                            mgmt_addr = 'fao.sentinelone.net'
                            limit 1000
